Version 1.0
-----------
  * It is probably a good idea to save every now and then, just in
    case :-)  In particular, save after you zifmia/vaxum the
    adventurer, since sometimes it takes a while for him to show up.

  * If you have cut-and-paste capability you can just cut and paste
    each line below; the periods seperate the commands and Enchanter
    will understand that.

    Don't put more items on the short lines; they're broken there for
    a reason: Enchanter will ignore any commands on the same line
    after something important happens, so you don't miss it by
    accident.  Also when you talk to the turtle he'll think any
    additional commands on the same line are more commands to him.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    se. se. ne. s.

    gnusto rezrov. ne. ne. nw. nw. sw. n. open oven. take bread and jug.
    s. ne. se. ne. fill jug with water. drink water. frotz jug.
    learn rezrov and rezrov. sw. se. e. e. rezrov gate. e. n. n. u.
    take egg. d. s. s. s. s. e. drop jug. e. move lighted portrait.
    take scroll. gnusto ozmoo. learn ozmoo. w. take jug. n. drop all. n.
    e. e.

    ozmoo me. wait. d. w. w. s. take all except box. rezrov egg.
    cut rope with dagger. open box. take scroll. gnusto melbor.
    learn melbor. melbor me. drop dagger. s. d. open door. n. move block.
    e. take scroll. gnusto exex. w. eat bread. s. u. e. e. n. n.
    drink water. n. n. examine tracks. reach into hole. gnusto gondar. s.
    s. s. s. w. w. w. u. get in bed. get up. examine bedpost.
    press button. take scroll. gnusto vaxum.
    learn nitfol and exex and rezrov and rezrov. d. e. e. e. n. n. n. n.
    n. rezrov gate. n. take scroll. gnusto krebf. e. look under pad.
    gnusto cleesh. w. s. eat bread. learn krebf. krebf shredded scroll.
    gnusto zifmia. learn zifmia and vaxum. drink water. drop bread. w.

<< Wander e and w up and down the 4 Halls until you see the >>
<< adventurer in a mirror, then:                            >>

    zifmia adventurer. vaxum adventurer. show egg to adventurer.

<< Go east again until you get to the Gaurded Door >>

    drop egg. adventurer, open door. u. take map and pencil. d. w.
    take bread. s. s. s. s. s. w. w. d. d. s. e. draw line from p to f.
    erase line from p to f. erase line from m to v.
    draw line from m to p. se. take scroll. nw. w. n.
    drop map and pencil. u. u. drink water. eat bread. w. u. get in bed.
    get up. d. e. e. e.
    learn cleesh and gondar and nitfol and exex and frotz. s. se.
    nitfol turtle. turtle, follow me.

    nw. n. e. u. exex turtle. turtle, se then take scroll then nw.

    take scroll. d. w. n. n. n. e. frotz me.
    drop all except powerful scroll and brittle scroll. e. kulcad stairs.
    izyuk me. e. gondar dragon. cleesh shape. guncho krill.

    quit.


